EN: My family comes from different cultural backgrounds.

ZH: 家庭聚餐是我们团聚的时刻。
EN: Family dinners are the moments when we gather together.

ZH: 家庭是我们最坚实的后盾。
EN: Family is our strongest support.

ZH: 我的家庭在乡村里有一间小屋。
EN: My family has a small house in the countryside.

ZH: 家庭是最初的社会。
EN: Family is the basic unit of society.

ZH: 家庭在人生中扮演着重要的角色。
EN: Family plays an important role in life.

ZH: 我的家庭对我有很大的影响。
EN: My family has a great influence on me.

ZH: 家庭是一个温馨的港湾。
EN: Family is a warm harbor.

ZH: 我的家庭一直很支持我的决定。
EN: My family has always supported my decisions.

ZH: 家庭是一个相互尊重的单位。
EN: Family is a unit of mutual respect.

ZH: 我的家庭有很强的凝聚力。
EN: My family has a strong sense of cohesion.

ZH: 家庭是孩子们的第一个学校。
EN: Family is the first school for children.

ZH: 我的家庭信奉传统价值观。
EN: My family adheres to traditional values.

ZH: 家庭是爱和包容的归宿。
EN: Family is the home of love and tolerance.

ZH: 我的家庭经历了很多挑战。
EN: My family has gone through many challenges.

ZH: 家庭是我们生活中最珍贵的财富。
EN: Family is the most precious wealth in our lives.

ZH: 我的家庭教育我勤劳和诚实。
EN: My family taught me to be hardworking and honest.

ZH: 家庭是我生命中最重要的一部分。
EN: Family is the most important part of my life.
